/use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3617278\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 20, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104yvx1665702629417.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yvx1665702629417.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/yvx1665702629417.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"yvx1665702629417\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Color of the label text when the widget, tab, or menu item is selected. If not specified, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Foreground Color</span> is used.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__p_d101702e1_d101703e1_d101704e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n         \n                                ForecolorSelect\n                                <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">RGBColor</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__table_d11969e1_d11970e1_d11971e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__table_d11969e1_d11970e1_d11971e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__table_d11969e1_d11970e1_d11971e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvx1665702629417__table_d11969e1_d11970e1_d11971e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvx1665702629417__table_d11969e1_d11970e1_d11971e1__entry__2\">Name of a web color or system color. For more\n                     information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rcm1665702587635.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rcm1665702587635.html\" title=\"Uniface supports standard color definitions including system colors as defined by the operating system, Web colors defined by the W3C, and RGB (red-green-blue) colors expressed in hex or decimal numbers. Any of these color definitions can be used when defining the value of foreground and background colors of components, widgets, panels, and toolbars.\">Standard Colors</a>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvx1665702629417__table_d11969e1_d11970e1_d11971e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">HexColorNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"yvx1665702629417__table_d11969e1_d11970e1_d11971e1__entry__2\">Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a\n                     color.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__section_tws_yhf_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d593970e131\">CommandButton</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__p_d101708e1_d101709e1_d101710e1\">For the Command Button widget, this property only\n        works if the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Representation</span> property is set to\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__section_pyx_zhf_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d593970e146\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__pre_k4f_b3f_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"forecolorselect=#0000FF\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__section_txj_b3f_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d593970e155\">Menu</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__p_d101717e1_d101718e1_d101719e1\">For menus, this property also determines the color of\n        separators in menus. It can only be set in the application initialization file and applies\n        to all menus. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__pre_lg4_f3f_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">menu=umenu(forecolor=black;ForeColorSelect=green)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__section_rms_f3f_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d593970e168\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__ul_pzw_g3f_vwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__li_d41231e1_d41232e1_d41233e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__li_d41234e1_d41235e1_d41236e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gzs1665702629046.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gzs1665702629046.html\" title=\"The (ucolorlist) widget displays a list of system or web colors for selection in a form component. Uniface provides a logical widget called ColorList, which is mapped to ucolorlist.\">ucolorlist (ColorList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__li_d41237e1_d41238e1_d41239e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fud1688450548955.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fud1688450548955.html\" title=\"The udropdownlist widget is a field-level widget that can display a list of valid options in a list below the input field, so that the user can select one. It is applicable only to form components.\">udropdownlist (DropDownList)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__li_d41240e1_d41241e1_d41242e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rez1688451198680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rez1688451198680.html\" title=\"The ulistbox widget is a field-level widget that displays an open list in which one or more values can be selected. It can only be used in form components.\">ulistbox (ListBox )</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__li_d41243e1_d41244e1_d41245e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"yvx1665702629417__li_d41246e1_d41247e1_d41248e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vfw1705577424699.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vfw1705577424699.html\" title=\"Uniface enables you to define menu bar, drop-down menu, and pop-up menu objects for use in Windows applications.\">Menu Objects</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/btj1665702631955.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Representation</a><p>This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617278\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617278\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Active Foreground Color (ForecolorSelect) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 20, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Color of the label text when the widget, tab, or menu item is selected. If not specified, the Foreground Color is used. \" ForecolorSelect = ColorName | HexColorNumber | RGBColor \" Value Description ColorName Name of a web color or system color. For more information, see Standard Colors . HexColorNumber Hexadecimal number (prefixed by a hash mark) of a color. CommandButton For the Command Button widget, this property only works if the Representation property is set to Uniface . Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(FLD1) = \"forecolorselect=#0000FF\" Copy Menu For menus, this property also determines the color of separators in menus. It can only be set in the application initialization file and applies to all menus. For example: menu=umenu(forecolor=black;ForeColorSelect=green) Copy Applies To CommandButton ucolorlist (ColorList) udropdownlist (DropDownList) ulistbox (ListBox ) utabex (TabEx) Menu Objects Related Links Representation This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}